'''Pròiseact nan Ealan''' is the [[Scotland|Scottish]] [[Scottish Gaelic language|Gaelic]] arts agency. It was set up in 1987 for the development of the [[Scottish Gaelic]] arts. Based in [[Stornoway, Outer Hebrides|Stornoway]], [[Isle of Lewis]] it is a [[not for profit]] [[limited company]] and [[Charitable organization|charity]]. Its projects have won many awards including foreign [[film festivals]] and its best known project is [[An Leabhar Mòr]].

